# Paramount Launchpad - Cursor AI Rules

## Project Overview
Paramount Launchpad is an AI-powered liquor wholesale onboarding system that transforms the overwhelming 19,000-product catalog into a personalized experience for new customers. The system addresses the critical problem where 30% of new customers never place their first order due to catalog complexity.

## Architecture
- **Backend**: Node.js + TypeScript + Express with Clean Architecture
- **Frontend**: React.js + TypeScript + Vite with Clean Architecture
- **Database**: MongoDB with Mongoose
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **State Management**: React hooks (can be extended with Zustand)

